txt.en: Deliver the sand-scarred ears to a collection box
Wanted: sand-scarred ears from the Ikorbân Valley. Gather them to earn a reward suitable for collectors.
The Adúrhid have posted a task to collect sand-scarred ears. These can be turned in for a reward.
You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Ikorbân Valley Adúrhid Task: Sand-scarred Ear
Wanted: sand-scarred ears from the Ikorbân Valley.
You have accepted a task to acquire sand-scarred ears for the Adúrhid.
